Welcome to the Super Entity Game Server! SEGS is under active development and is far from being feature complete.<br>
<br>
Please consider contributing to our success by reporting bugs on our github and joining our community on Discord:<br>
<face heading>
<span align=center><a href="https://github.com/Segs/">https://github.com/Segs/</a> and <a href="https://discord.segs.dev">https://discord.segs.dev/</a></span>
