<br>
<color SteelBlue>Latest Changes:</color><br>
- Tasks, Contacts, Clues, Souvenirs, Emails, Stores (test with LuaBot)
- Lua Scripting of simple mission like "hide-and-seek" and "timed races"
- Spawn Pedestrians, Cars, Blimps, Contacts, Basic Encounters in Outbreak, Atlas Park, King's Row, Steel Canyon, Skyway City, Talos Island, Independence Port, Perez Park, Boomtown and Dark Astoria.
- Some Door Transfers
- Tailor and Multiple Costumes
- Preliminary Powers (Pew Pew Pew!)
- To fully utilize powers, make sure the server has a /data/powers.json
- AdminRPC and RPC support
- SEGSAdmin improvements
- Output log improvements
- Many improvements to how we store/load characters and data from the database.
- Bug Fixes
<br>
<color SandyBrown>Useful Slash Commands:</color><br>
<color BurlyWood><i>/stuck</i></color>  - resets your character to the starting location in current map<br>
<color BurlyWood><i>/moveto x y z</i></color>  - move character to the x y z coordinates<br>
<color BurlyWood><i>/fly</i></color>  - toggles the "flying" flag for your character<br>
<color BurlyWood><i>/mapmenu</i></color>  - Shows a menu that allows you to change maps (zones)<br>
<color BurlyWood><i>/train</i></color>  - train up to the next level! Make sure you have enough XP<br>
<color BurlyWood><i>/cmdlist</i></color>  - list all available slash commands<br>
